                </p>
                <p class="probably-seen__person-title">
                    – Marion D., Lyon
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="probably-seen__card swiper-slide">
                <img loading="lazy" class="probably-seen__person" src="{{ 'review-image-2.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Reviews">
                <img loading="lazy" src="{{ 'reviews-star.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Reviews">
                <p>
                    Je recommande UVlizer à tous mes amis. En voyage ou à la maison, je l'ai toujours sur moi pour désinfecter en quelques secondes.
                </p>
                <p class="probably-seen__person-title">
                    – Jérôme P., Paris
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="probably-seen__card swiper-slide">
                <img loading="lazy" class="probably-seen__person" src="{{ 'review-image-3.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Reviews">
                <img loading="lazy" src="{{ 'reviews-star.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Reviews">
                <p>
                    I bought two of them, they were delivered in less than a week. Only used it twice so far, in my Master bedroom and guest bedroom, the rooms had a clean smell to them.
                </p>
                <p class="probably-seen__person-title">
                    - Sharon L.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
    </div>

    <p class="probably-seen__title">
        Ils parlent de nous
    </p>

    <div class="slider-container probably-seen__partners">
        <div class="swiper-wrapper">
            <div class="probably-seen__partners-card swiper-slide">
                <img loading="lazy" class="probably-seen__partners-image" src="{{ 'partners-1.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Partners image">
            </div>
            <div class="probably-seen__partners-card swiper-slide">
                <img loading="lazy" class="probably-seen__partners-image" src="{{ 'partners-2.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Partners image">
            </div>
            <div class="probably-seen__partners-card swiper-slide">
                <img loading="lazy" class="probably-seen__partners-image" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0519/0238/2231/files/Group_2672.png?v=1733837770" alt="Partners image">
            </div>
            <div class="probably-seen__partners-card swiper-slide">
                <img loading="lazy" class="probably-seen__partners-image" src="{{ 'partners-4.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Partners image">
            </div>
            <div class="probably-seen__partners-card swiper-slide">
                <img loading="lazy" class="probably-seen__partners-image" src="{{ 'partners-5.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Partners image">
            </div>
            <div class="probably-seen__partners-card swiper-slide">
                <img loading="lazy" class="probably-seen__partners-image" src="{{ 'partners-6.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Partners image">
            </div>
            <div class="probably-seen__partners-card swiper-slide">
                <img loading="lazy" class="probably-seen__partners-image" src="{{ 'partners-7.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Partners image">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p class="bottom-text">“Je recommande UVlizer à tous mes amis. En voyage ou à la maison, je l'ai toujours sur moi pour désinfecter en quelques secondes.”</p>
</section>